IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the undersigned have executed this Amendment Agreement on the date set forth above.

TORCHLIGHT ENERGY RESOURCES, INC.


/s/ Thomas Lapinski                                           
By:  Thomas Lapinski, Chief Executive Officer



/s/ John A. Brda                                                 
John A. Brda



